    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 mt-10">What Conversions to Track</h3>

    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Track one primary conversion that represents real value — the closest thing you have to revenue:
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <span class="text-coral mt-0.5">&#9656;</span>
        <p><strong class="text-white">Free trial signups</strong> — if your product has a trial, this is your primary conversion. Someone in your trial is a potential paying customer.</p>
