        <span class="text-coral font-mono text-xs mt-0.5">03</span>
        <p>Choose <strong class="text-white">"Page load"</strong> — fire the conversion when the user lands on your thank-you or success page (e.g., /welcome, /signup/success)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <span class="text-coral font-mono text-xs mt-0.5">04</span>
        <p>Install the Google Ads tag on your site (via Google Tag Manager or a script tag), then add the conversion event snippet to your success page only</p>
      </div>
