        <span class="text-coral font-mono text-xs mt-0.5">3.</span>
        <p><strong class="text-white">Is cost-per-conversion economically viable?</strong> If you paid $100 for 2 signups, your CAC is $50. Is that acceptable given your product's pricing and LTV? If yes, scale up. If no, focus on improving landing page conversion rate before spending more.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-coral/10 to-transparent border-l-4 border-coral pl-6 py-4 rounded-r-lg">
